rows.label: tlk000023_msg0001
rows.name:
To think that I would end up traveling
on the same Divine Beast ship as the
Heaven's Holy Grail and her Driver.

rows.label: tlk000023_msg0002
rows.name:
Rest assured. I have no intention
of causing any trouble.

rows.label: tlk000023_msg0003
rows.name:
For now, I shall simply observe
where you are all headed.
